notes.note: Received estimate from Halton Transmission for replacement of timing chain and intake cam shaft. Requested customer's original concern, findings during diag, and all maintenance receipts. Waiting for response. M.P.
notes.content: Received estimate from Halton Transmission for replacement of timing chain and intake cam shaft. Requested customer's original concern, findings during diag, and all maintenance receipts. Waiting for response. M.P.

notes.note: Adam from Halton Transmission responded this am. Customer came in due to check engine light on. Received all maintenance receipts, look good. Spoke to Adam, says he is not sure if the vvt cam gear broke and took out the chain or if the chain experienced normal wear and tear. Going to take off the timing cover and check for broken guides (common on these vehicles). If guide is broken, guide is the reason for additional wear on chain. If not, then chain experience normal wear and will not be covered. M.P.
